Spatiales (the French Spatial Agency), the Canadian Space Agency and the
United Kingdom Space Agency, with launch planned in late 2020. SWOT is
both a continental hydrology and oceanography mission. However, only the
hydrology capabilities of SWOT are discussed here. After a description
of the SWOT mission requirements and measurement capabilities, we review
the SWOT-related studies concerning land hydrology published to date.
